- Sir?

01:14:17.620 --> 01:14:18.788
<i>...because,
the more I think about it...</i>

01:14:56.826 --> 01:14:57.911
Mom?

01:14:59.204 --> 01:15:00.205
Shh.

01:15:03.208 --> 01:15:04.792
<i>Thank you, wife.</i>

01:15:07.170 --> 01:15:09.339
<i>My offspring,
how were your days?</i>

01:15:12.175 --> 01:15:13.259
