but in the same house?

01:16:20.910 --> 01:16:23.454
As long as it doesn't
complain to Shirley.

01:16:24.914 --> 01:16:26.124
<i>Cut it, wife.</i>

01:16:28.167 --> 01:16:30.586
<i>As you did before.</i>

01:16:30.586 --> 01:16:32.839
